{"tid":150070,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我幫你就得，你幫我就唔得？","createTime":"2017-03-09T17:46:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T19:38:27.000Z","uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15c6070c91cd5f3098bf62ef8cfa73c5808f6d51","tid":150070,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:46:07.000Z","msg":"我真係好唔明"},{"pid":"4667f66c614a5f621b06d1835a6ca98fd86c3658","tid":150070,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:46:56.000Z","msg":"我幾時先有老死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7fe591fbc892dd91a4544a2aef67c4edadef5ea","tid":150070,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:47:29.000Z","msg":"人係自私嘅"},{"pid":"31bd67592dc3967116d140a112222009546beef6","tid":150070,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:48:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人係自私嘅</blockquote><br />\n我知，但都唔完全係"},{"pid":"9dc6cc4f5199bdbec340c1ad993aa8aef272695f","tid":150070,"uid":89953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:50:29.000Z","msg":"所以我睇人幫"},{"pid":"8e20b8d96ab52daddb510500aee1214181fffde9","tid":150070,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:50:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人係自私嘅</blockquote><br />\n我知，但都唔完全係</blockquote><br />\n咁改一改，香港人係自私嘅<br />\nGrad後無真心朋友係基本<br />\n已經做好覺悟"},{"pid":"83671353e100edb2908703b35f1857869f8922f5","tid":150070,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:50:58.000Z","msg":"嘻嘻哈哈既朋友係有，但當你有難困我會幫你，但當我有小小困難，都唔係大問題，你都唔幫我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ddd2017fc6b5dc72395c9eae3c46ffed8d1bf54","tid":150070,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:51:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人係自私嘅</blockquote><br />\n我知，但都唔完全係</blockquote><br />\n咁改一改，香港人係自私嘅<br />\nGrad後無真心朋友係基本<br />\n已經做好覺悟</blockquote><br />\n未grad都無"},{"pid":"cf538b44a0534be348636c8df94492cae29e9680","tid":150070,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:52:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人係自私嘅</blockquote><br />\n我知，但都唔完全係</blockquote><br />\n咁改一改，香港人係自私嘅<br />\nGrad後無真心朋友係基本<br />\n已經做好覺悟</blockquote><br />\n未grad都無</blockquote><br />\n我諗應該得返中學Friend係真心"},{"pid":"c5784331919005a790b5d4815fe5793acb3e2288","tid":150070,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以我睇人幫</blockquote><br />\n我都唔知，總之我意識到朋友有困難，我知佢會好無助，所以我會幫下佢"},{"pid":"97607cb8f948f545c972a2b498a4ad35ee6fc314","tid":150070,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:56:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>所以我睇人幫</blockquote><br />\n我都唔知，總之我意識到朋友有困難，我知佢會好無助，所以我會幫下佢</blockquote><br />\n我會衡量下佢嘅往跡係咪值得我去幫"},{"pid":"f1d7bd2dbab84dade6c04bb9621d5c7e097fce85","tid":150070,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:56:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人係自私嘅</blockquote><br />\n我知，但都唔完全係</blockquote><br />\n咁改一改，香港人係自私嘅<br />\nGrad後無真心朋友係基本<br />\n已經做好覺悟</blockquote><br />\n未grad都無</blockquote><br />\n我諗應該得返中學Friend係真心</blockquote><br />\n咁你好彩囉，真心應該係有既，不過有啲朋友真係淨係顧自己，所以我都算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45834489e96bdc0cdd82665d0780a58ef059eb21","tid":150070,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:58:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>所以我睇人幫</blockquote><br />\n我都唔知，總之我意識到朋友有困難，我知佢會好無助，所以我會幫下佢</blockquote><br />\n我會衡量下佢嘅往跡係咪值得我去幫</blockquote><br />\n應該咁講，其實佢地係平時身邊啲朋友來，有咩我都盡力幫，依家我都開始有啲你咁既諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c4d30f5d6bf8cfd3255d146eb628a438d33fc0","tid":150070,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通係我要求太高？雖然老土，但朋友之間既互相幫助唔係最基本咩"},{"pid":"528acf45845d44b87364c62742b7037fe00c26ff","tid":150070,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:02:55.000Z","msg":"有無人比我叫下春<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6828e4d480acd650371c953c98e51146f58d72","tid":150070,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/10/020523_6b9a90f81e33c0fe891154e27cb62f20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F10%2F020523_6b9a90f81e33c0fe891154e27cb62f20.jpg&h=ad7b6196&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66eb7c9a0db1b685ca39c1973dc480ad54b2777d","tid":150070,"uid":46,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:06:19.000Z","msg":"所以我依家唔會點幫人<br />\n唔幫你都會比人話我小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你一句多謝 唔該都冇<br />\n好似老奉咁<br />\n我寧願你話我小氣好過<br />\n真係幫嘅剩係得返啲肯定會睇到有利益嘅會利用到對方"},{"pid":"8e4cbe89c89b9190c4ad56e52d6e6659ca5db88d","tid":150070,"uid":5955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:07:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通係我要求太高？雖然老土，但朋友之間既互相幫助唔係最基本咩</blockquote><br />\n我諗如果係舉手之勞，好多人都肯幫<br />\n要求再高d就要睇你同人幾熟喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a8baa46f2d406d13544f3e81d80390fcaa018e4","tid":150070,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:09:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以我依家唔會點幫人<br />\n唔幫你都會比人話我小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你一句多謝 唔該都冇<br />\n好似老奉咁<br />\n我寧願你話我小氣好過<br />\n真係幫嘅剩係得返啲肯定會睇到有利益嘅會利用到對方</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁你有無老死"},{"pid":"baa016b5210f5afd2be12ff363f43042715d3a49","tid":150070,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:11:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通係我要求太高？雖然老土，但朋友之間既互相幫助唔係最基本咩</blockquote><br />\n我諗如果係舉手之勞，好多人都肯幫<br />\n要求再高d就要睇你同人幾熟喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實平時我都幫佢唔少嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我個啲對於佢來講係舉手之勞都唔幫，要我主動開到口<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17910ca88a8a284c7c5a7e6ca7f3f3ac126a647f","tid":150070,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:14:20.000Z","msg":"算啦，順其自然啦，訓覺先<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9653ae629361aa74f861a5d777b56cd8ee23eb6","tid":150070,"uid":72477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:14:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通係我要求太高？雖然老土，但朋友之間既互相幫助唔係最基本咩</blockquote><br />\n我諗如果係舉手之勞，好多人都肯幫<br />\n要求再高d就要睇你同人幾熟喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實平時我都幫佢唔少嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我個啲對於佢來講係舉手之勞都唔幫，<span style=\"color: red;\">要我主動開到口</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人地都射完爽完，就梗係拍拍蘿柚走啦<br />\n唔通仲開口幫返你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487eb8026466a7b6e21442258b28284ee07901ed","tid":150070,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/10/021500_866ae307217d3944e084f62ff2341507.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F10%2F021500_866ae307217d3944e084f62ff2341507.jpg&h=7a47b447&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7c09eed02b2f874f870bb1a88aa7ccc5828685f","tid":150070,"uid":46,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:15:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>所以我依家唔會點幫人<br />\n唔幫你都會比人話我小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你一句多謝 唔該都冇<br />\n好似老奉咁<br />\n我寧願你話我小氣好過<br />\n真係幫嘅剩係得返啲肯定會睇到有利益嘅會利用到對方</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁你有無老死</blockquote><br />\n有<br />\n咁有啲都會幫下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上次比人屌我小氣係因為佢覺得我老奉要幫佢<br />\n同埋本身都有啲討厭嗰個人<br />\n個格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7012d81536f6c02a1ca165e08f228ec00d3e3c","tid":150070,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:16:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通係我要求太高？雖然老土，但朋友之間既互相幫助唔係最基本咩</blockquote><br />\n我諗如果係舉手之勞，好多人都肯幫<br />\n要求再高d就要睇你同人幾熟喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實平時我都幫佢唔少嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我個啲對於佢來講係舉手之勞都唔幫，<span style=\"color: red;\">要我主動開到口</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人地都射完爽完，就梗係拍拍蘿柚走啦<br />\n唔通仲開口幫返你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吓，我會幫囉，小小野姐，計到咁撚盡咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}